# Excluded from the published tarball.
# `package.json#files` already restricts publish entry points; npm walks
# the contents of those allowlisted dirs WITHOUT applying this root-level
# .npmignore for sub-paths. So sub-directory exclusions live in their own
# .npmignore files:
#   - hooks/.npmignore   → drops dev-only hooks/tests/ harness
#   - skills/.npmignore  → drops *-workspace/ runtime artefacts
# This file only has to cover root-level noise.

.DS_Store
*.swp
